data.title: Matte Babel - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Matte Babel: her birthday, what she did before fame, her family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

First became known hosting MuchMusic's Much On Demand and later reporting on CP24. He then became a correspondent on Entertainment Tonight Canada in 2011. He also hosted the reality program Canada Sings.

Before Fame

He earned degrees in sociology and communications before embarking on a short career in semi-professional football in Austria.

Trivia

He has interviewed countless superstars on the red carpet, from Tom Cruise to Justin Timberlake.

Family Life

He was born and raised in Toronto, Canada. He has been dating actress Shay Mitchell and the two welcomed a daughter named Atlas together in 2019. On February 8th, 2022, the couple announced that they were expecting their second child together. They welcomed their second daughter in June 2022.
